      "text": "大会が終わった後もなかなか予定が合わなくて……\n今日は久しぶりに二人で出掛けられると思ったのにな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and even after the tournament‚ we couldn’t find a time that worked…\nI was looking forward to hanging out‚ just the two of us‚ for the first time in a while~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.2666658404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
